               <p>On the 5th of October I was going on <placeName id="t17861213-26-crimeloc139">Fleet-market</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17861213-26-crimeloc139" type="placeName" value="Fleet-market"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17861213-26-crimeloc139" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-26-off137 t17861213-26-crimeloc139"></join>, and I perceived somebody at my pocket; I turned round and caught the prisoner putting my handkerchief into his bosom; I took it from him; I believe it to be mine; a constable was coming by, and took him into custody; he said, he did it for want.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17861213-26-person281">
                  SAMUEL
                   ROBERTS
               <interp inst="t17861213-26-person281" type="surname" value="ROBERTS"></interp>
