                     <interp inst="t17861213-26-person281" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner following the gentleman, and I took him into custody.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I picked up the handkerchief; the gentleman would have let me go, but Roberts said, I was as good a twenty shillings as ever he handled.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17861213-26-verdict140" type="verdictDescription">
